{"id":256354,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/酷6拍客-篮球奶奶的辛酸生活/","date":"2012-10-11T10:01:25Z","modified":"2012-10-11T10:01:25Z","title":"酷6拍客 | “篮球奶奶”的辛酸生活","content":"<p>浙江金华，有位传奇老人，她叫朱淑媚，今年76岁，因其酷爱篮球，投篮命中率极高，而被人称为“篮球奶奶”。球场上的老人生龙活虎但在现实生活里，朱奶奶却说 “我不是幸福的”。老奶奶今年76岁，因驼背身高仅1米5，但球龄已20多年，还能爬杆。她生活坎坷，53岁离婚，生活费每月400多元，无房，女儿有精神疾病未嫁，由她照顾。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><object width=\"480\" height=\"400\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://player.ku6.com/refer/kDD_Bvjr1T1Lh_aiDK44nQ../v.swf\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"flashvars\" value=\"from=ku6\" /><embed width=\"480\" height=\"400\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" src=\"http://player.ku6.com/refer/kDD_Bvjr1T1Lh_aiDK44nQ../v.swf\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" flashvars=\"from=ku6\" /></object></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">视频<a href=\"http://v.ku6.com/special/show_6586810/kDD_Bvjr1T1Lh_aiDK44nQ...html#\" target=\"_blank\">地址</a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18269,13770],"tags":[20522]}